modules.name: Control.Monad.Eff.JQuery
modules.comments:
This module defines foreign types and functions for working with 
the jQuery library.

declarations.comments: The type of collections of jQuery-wrapped nodes.
declarations.title: JQuery

declarations.comments: A type synonym to help readability of type signatures.
declarations.title: Selector

declarations.comments: Run a function when the document is loaded.
declarations.title: ready

declarations.comments: Find child nodes matching a selector
declarations.title: find

declarations.comments: Find the closest element matching the selector.
declarations.title: closest

declarations.comments: Test if an element has a CSS class.
declarations.title: hasClass

declarations.comments: Append the first node as a child node of the second.
declarations.title: append

declarations.comments: Append text as a child node.
declarations.title: appendText

declarations.comments: Get the text content of an element.
declarations.title: getText

declarations.comments: Set the text content of an element.
declarations.title: setText

declarations.comments: Get the value of a form element.
declarations.title: getValue

declarations.comments: Set the value of a form element.
declarations.title: setValue

declarations.comments: Set the visibility of an element.
declarations.title: setVisible

declarations.comments: Register an event handler for elements matching a selector.
declarations.title: on'

declarations.comments: Prevent the default action for an event.
declarations.title: preventDefault
